   764тЖТdef make_safe_parse_float(parse_float: ParseFloat) -> ParseFloat:
   765тЖТ    """A decorator to make `parse_float` safe.
   766тЖТ
   767тЖТ    `parse_float` must not return dicts or lists, because these types
